WEBVTT

00:00:00.096 --> 00:01:00.096

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.980
Episode 11

00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:35.200
Wow, this crab is huge!

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:36.230
Ms. Fang,

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:37.480
would you like this?

00:01:38.150 --> 00:01:38.760
Whelk.

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:40.350
It's delicious.

00:01:40.950 --> 00:01:42.310
How about this lobster?

00:01:42.510 --> 00:01:44.070
It's huge.

00:01:44.070 --> 00:01:45.040
It's very rare.

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:47.350
Ms. Fang,

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:50.560
please stop refusing.

00:01:50.590 --> 00:01:52.430
We need to eat.

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:58.230
This is too simple.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:01:59.590
Ms. Fang,

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:01.590
you don't need to save me money.

00:02:02.310 --> 00:02:03.150
It's just us.

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:04.150
Ordering too much would be a waste.

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:07.640
No wonder my dad

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:08.630
likes you so much.

00:02:09.430 --> 00:02:11.560
You truly have excellent character.

00:02:13.430 --> 00:02:14.280
Ms. Fang,

00:02:14.630 --> 00:02:16.910
I heard you haven't found a job yet.

00:02:18.960 --> 00:02:20.360
Could I hire you

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:21.150
as the deputy general manager

00:02:21.150 --> 00:02:22.470
of my company?

00:02:24.710 --> 00:02:26.560
You don't know me.

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:27.840
Why do you think

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:28.400
I'm capable

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:29.680
of such an important position?

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:31.960
It's actually very simple.

00:02:32.590 --> 00:02:33.470
My company

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:36.800
has scheduling, finance,

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:37.750
and logistics.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:39.430
We don't need more people.

00:02:39.710 --> 00:02:40.310
You'd only need

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:42.120
to manage them.

00:02:42.590 --> 00:02:44.360
Since you don't need more people

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:45.750
and the company is running smoothly,

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:48.000
why do you need a manager?

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:49.560
Because I need one.

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:52.800
Ms. Fang,

00:02:53.630 --> 00:02:54.560
I've told you before.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.400
I'm divorced.

00:02:59.030 --> 00:03:00.280
It's been five years.

00:03:00.630 --> 00:03:02.520
I was very poor before,

00:03:02.750 --> 00:03:03.590
so my ex-wife

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:05.030
ran off with another man.

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.360
Now I'm rich.

00:03:06.710 --> 00:03:07.590
My dad

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:09.680
wants me to pursue you.

00:03:10.430 --> 00:03:11.310
So this deputy

00:03:11.310 --> 00:03:12.560
general manager position

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:14.800
is reserved for your future wife?

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:16.000
That's right!

00:03:16.190 --> 00:03:16.840
You'll be

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:18.120
Mrs. Jia from now on.

00:03:22.710 --> 00:03:23.520
And you think

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:24.960
I'll agree?

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:26.400
I have 30 cars.

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:28.630
Maybe 300 in the future.

00:03:28.870 --> 00:03:30.750
I also have 11 houses.

00:03:30.870 --> 00:03:32.870
Maybe 100 in the future.

00:03:35.470 --> 00:03:36.190
Yeah.

00:03:36.750 --> 00:03:37.280
Yeah?

00:03:37.590 --> 00:03:39.750
Transfer your cars

00:03:39.800 --> 00:03:40.870
and houses

00:03:40.870 --> 00:03:42.360
to my name,

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:43.750
and then I'll agree.

00:03:45.080 --> 00:03:47.120
Your future assets

00:03:47.190 --> 00:03:48.680
will also be transferred to my name.

00:03:48.680 --> 00:03:49.470
Okay?

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:05.030
Ms. Fang, are you not full?

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:06.430
I'm very full.

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:10.280
Shall I take you home?

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:11.080
Yeah.

00:04:13.030 --> 00:04:13.680
Yeah?

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:15.870
Yeah.

00:04:17.830 --> 00:04:18.830
This is the first time

00:04:18.830 --> 00:04:20.070
I've received such treatment.

00:04:20.680 --> 00:04:21.750
I'm the only passenger

00:04:21.750 --> 00:04:23.040
on the bus.

00:04:23.510 --> 00:04:24.920
I'm quite happy today.

00:04:25.870 --> 00:04:27.240
I'm glad you're happy.

00:04:30.430 --> 00:04:31.510
Ms. Fang,

00:04:32.510 --> 00:04:33.480
I think we can

00:04:33.480 --> 00:04:35.000
discuss this.

00:04:35.270 --> 00:04:36.040
How about

00:04:36.390 --> 00:04:37.600
I give you two cars

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:40.120
and transfer two houses

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:41.000
to your name?

00:04:41.310 --> 00:04:42.720
What do you think?

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:43.600
You think

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.870
I'm bargaining with you?

00:04:46.480 --> 00:04:47.360
I'm sorry, Ms. Fang.

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:47.830
I...

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:49.000
Let me tell you,

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:50.240
marriage should

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:52.360
be based on love.

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:53.630
And love

00:04:53.870 --> 00:04:55.600
isn't just about cars

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:56.480
and houses.

00:05:22.310 --> 00:05:23.870
Okay. You can go check over there.

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:29.800
Sir,

00:05:29.920 --> 00:05:31.240
could I have an application form?

00:05:31.480 --> 00:05:32.750
We only accept postgraduate
degree applicants.

00:05:32.830 --> 00:05:33.390
Okay.

00:05:34.870 --> 00:05:36.070
Finance and Economics.

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:38.040
Everyone!

00:05:38.190 --> 00:05:39.680
Look here!

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:42.240
To establish yourself and
get promoted in Shenzhen,

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:43.830
you can't rely on just opportunities.

00:05:44.190 --> 00:05:45.560
The Academy of Continuing Education

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:47.430
can help you get your ticket,

00:05:47.630 --> 00:05:49.600
your stepping stone to the workplace.

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:51.390
Self-study or correspondence
courses are available.

00:05:51.390 --> 00:05:53.070
Evening classes and full-time
programs are both offered.

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:54.870
A degree is paramount

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:56.720
for finding a good job!

00:05:57.160 --> 00:05:57.830
Come on and check.

00:05:57.870 --> 00:05:58.920
Academy of Continuing Education.

00:05:58.920 --> 00:05:59.270
Come on,

00:05:59.870 --> 00:06:00.430
here.

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:03.870
Fang Wanzhi?

00:06:08.680 --> 00:06:09.190
I've been looking

00:06:09.390 --> 00:06:10.510
for you since the talent market

00:06:10.510 --> 00:06:11.240
opened on the 6th.

00:06:11.510 --> 00:06:13.070
You finally came today.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:14.190
Haven't you

00:06:14.190 --> 00:06:15.390
already finished your task?

00:06:16.070 --> 00:06:17.360
It's a new year.

00:06:17.390 --> 00:06:18.630
The recruitment workload is heavier.

00:06:19.390 --> 00:06:20.600
I can barely breathe.

00:06:20.600 --> 00:06:21.800
My voice is hoarse.

00:06:22.190 --> 00:06:22.680
So I'd like

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:24.630
to recruit you first.

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:26.630
I told you not

00:06:26.630 --> 00:06:27.720
to try and make tuition money off me.

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:29.310
You still won't given up.

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:30.680
You misunderstood.

00:06:31.070 --> 00:06:31.750
I want

00:06:31.750 --> 00:06:32.560
to recruit you

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:34.240
as a staff member to assist
me with recruitment.

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:36.240
In other words,

00:06:36.680 --> 00:06:38.040
I want to give you a job.

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:39.240
Not a temporary one.

00:06:39.510 --> 00:06:40.190
I've already spoken

00:06:40.190 --> 00:06:41.000
to HR

00:06:41.510 --> 00:06:42.270
and secured a permanent position

00:06:42.270 --> 00:06:43.040
for you.

00:06:47.720 --> 00:06:49.800
Are you interested?

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:51.950
Come on.

00:06:55.190 --> 00:06:56.750
Let me analyze you first.

00:06:57.830 --> 00:06:59.270
From the 6th until today,

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:01.310
you've been running around

00:07:01.390 --> 00:07:03.270
various talent markets and employers.

00:07:03.390 --> 00:07:03.870
Right?

00:07:04.750 --> 00:07:06.480
You haven't found a suitable job yet.

00:07:06.870 --> 00:07:07.630
Right?

00:07:08.070 --> 00:07:09.720
My predictions are very accurate.

00:07:10.190 --> 00:07:11.360
In your current state,

00:07:11.630 --> 00:07:13.310
you won't find a job anywhere.

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:15.720
What's wrong with me?

00:07:17.870 --> 00:07:19.560
Although you're trying hard to hide it,

00:07:19.870 --> 00:07:21.070
I can see the emptiness

00:07:21.070 --> 00:07:22.720
and weakness in your heart at a glance.

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:25.630
Your absent-minded,

00:07:25.630 --> 00:07:26.720
luck-seeking attitude

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:28.430
is a major taboo in job hunting.

00:07:28.750 --> 00:07:30.070
Job hunting isn't like shopping.

00:07:30.630 --> 00:07:31.870
Do you expect a great offer

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.480
to fall from the sky with this attitude?

00:07:33.630 --> 00:07:35.070
That's like a pipe dream.

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:36.480
It's impossible.

00:07:36.630 --> 00:07:37.430
I shouldn't have come

00:07:37.430 --> 00:07:38.390
to listen to your crap.

00:07:38.950 --> 00:07:40.310
Don't go. I've gone off on a tangent.

00:07:40.310 --> 00:07:41.190
Sorry.

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:42.870
I'd like

00:07:43.430 --> 00:07:44.390
to hire you as an

00:07:44.630 --> 00:07:46.600
admissions assistant at the Academy

00:07:46.750 --> 00:07:47.480
of Continuing Education.

00:07:50.390 --> 00:07:51.040
What about the salary?

00:07:51.830 --> 00:07:53.720
of course the base salary is not high.

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:55.120
So there's commission?

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:56.630
How will the tuition commission

00:07:56.830 --> 00:07:57.950
be split as your assistant?

00:07:59.480 --> 00:08:00.270
Commission?

00:08:01.070 --> 00:08:02.360
There's never been a
commission for admissions.

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:03.630
Don't lie to me.

00:08:03.630 --> 00:08:05.040
Would you be working so hard to cheat

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:05.950
if there were no commission?

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:06.950
Why are you

00:08:06.950 --> 00:08:08.240
being so rude?

00:08:08.360 --> 00:08:10.000
When have I cheated anyone?

00:08:10.310 --> 00:08:11.190
There really is no commission.

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:13.040
But there is a little overtime pay.

00:08:13.240 --> 00:08:14.870
For talent market admissions,

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:15.560
there's an eight-yuan

00:08:15.560 --> 00:08:16.920
transportation allowance

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:18.390
and a 12-yuan meal allowance per day.

00:08:25.070 --> 00:08:26.190
What will I do?

00:08:26.390 --> 00:08:28.000
That's the key point.

00:08:28.430 --> 00:08:29.510
I've decided to try
a different approach.

00:08:29.630 --> 00:08:30.680
You immediately came to mind.

00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:31.720
You have a

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:32.960
friendly image

00:08:33.030 --> 00:08:34.200
and your speech is engaging.

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:35.120
This plan

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:36.720
is tailor-made for you.

00:08:36.910 --> 00:08:37.550
Look at you.

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:39.870
You've been in Shenzhen
for less than a year,

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:41.870
but you've already failed miserably

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:42.720
in your job search,

00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:44.200
suffering numerous setbacks.

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:45.120
First,

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:46.390
you lack a diploma.

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:48.030
Your university dropout status

00:08:48.030 --> 00:08:48.630
on your resume

00:08:48.670 --> 00:08:50.550
is a joke in the talent market.

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:51.390
Isn't that a failure?

00:08:51.600 --> 00:08:52.030
Second,

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:53.440
you went to college,

00:08:53.480 --> 00:08:55.720
yet you can only find a menial job

00:08:55.750 --> 00:08:57.120
in a construction site canteen.

00:08:57.270 --> 00:08:57.840
Isn't that a failure?

00:08:57.840 --> 00:08:58.270
Third,

00:08:58.480 --> 00:08:59.550
because you haven't received

00:08:59.550 --> 00:09:00.320
professional guidance,

00:09:00.390 --> 00:09:01.630
you were helpless when facing

00:09:01.630 --> 00:09:02.720
financial disputes

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:03.670
with employers,

00:09:03.670 --> 00:09:04.960
even nearly causing a disaster.

00:09:05.080 --> 00:09:05.720
Isn't that a failure?

00:09:05.870 --> 00:09:06.360
Fourth,

00:09:06.630 --> 00:09:07.790
you wasted a golden opportunity

00:09:07.790 --> 00:09:08.630
to find a job

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:10.320
before the fierce competition among

00:09:10.320 --> 00:09:11.600
returning migrant workers began.

00:09:11.670 --> 00:09:13.000
That's another failure.

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:14.600
Go on.

00:09:14.870 --> 00:09:15.960
Do you know what I was thinking?

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:17.670
I print

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:19.440
more flyers

00:09:19.750 --> 00:09:21.600
and invite everyone who is confused

00:09:21.630 --> 00:09:23.150
and has similar experiences to you

00:09:23.270 --> 00:09:24.360
to come to our academy

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:25.390
to hear your sharing.

00:09:25.630 --> 00:09:27.120
This way, they can visit the school

00:09:27.270 --> 00:09:28.910
and learn from your failures,

00:09:28.960 --> 00:09:29.630
recognizing

00:09:29.670 --> 00:09:30.960
the importance

00:09:30.960 --> 00:09:31.510
of continuing education.

00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:33.790
Are you trying to use me
as a negative example

00:09:33.790 --> 00:09:34.870
to scam tuition fees from others?

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:36.630
How can this be called scamming?

00:09:36.750 --> 00:09:37.750
I'm helping them.

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:39.910
Let me tell you,

00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:40.720
first,

00:09:40.870 --> 00:09:42.000
not finishing university

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:43.200
was my own choice.

00:09:43.510 --> 00:09:44.000
Second,

00:09:44.120 --> 00:09:44.910
I found a cafeteria job

00:09:44.910 --> 00:09:45.550
as soon as

00:09:45.550 --> 00:09:46.630
I came Shenzhen

00:09:46.670 --> 00:09:48.000
and made my best friend.

00:09:48.030 --> 00:09:48.840
That's my luck.

00:09:49.150 --> 00:09:49.630
Third,

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.150
regarding the financial dispute,

00:09:51.150 --> 00:09:51.750
we could

00:09:51.750 --> 00:09:53.510
have resolved it without you.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:55.000
It didn't escalate into
anything serious.

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:56.080
Most importantly,

00:09:56.270 --> 00:09:57.910
today is my first time coming

00:09:57.910 --> 00:09:58.910
to the talent market since the New Year.

00:09:59.030 --> 00:10:00.360
For the past two weeks,

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:02.150
I've been offered high-paying jobs

00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:04.000
doing meaningful work every day.

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:07.840
Really?

00:10:07.910 --> 00:10:08.960
Of course.

00:10:09.030 --> 00:10:09.670
Finding a job

00:10:09.790 --> 00:10:11.150
in Shenzhen isn't difficult.

00:10:11.270 --> 00:10:12.720
Your theory of valuing
only education is a fallacy.

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:13.840
Don't try to fool me.

00:10:14.630 --> 00:10:15.150
Hey.

00:10:15.630 --> 00:10:16.910
I reject your offer.

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:19.030
I curse you to fail to meet your targets

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.240
and be fired soon.

00:10:22.030 --> 00:10:22.440
Hey.

00:10:22.510 --> 00:10:23.000
Don't go.

00:10:23.320 --> 00:10:24.320
Why do you leave?

00:10:24.600 --> 00:10:25.390
We can discuss it

00:10:25.390 --> 00:10:26.510
if you don't like this one.

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:28.750
Li, you made a fortune today!

00:10:28.790 --> 00:10:29.670
Yeah, that's right.

00:10:29.670 --> 00:10:31.120
So lucky!

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:34.080
Fang!

00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:36.360
You're back.

00:10:36.750 --> 00:10:37.320
Pei.

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:39.750
This house just

00:10:39.790 --> 00:10:41.000
brings good luck.

00:10:41.200 --> 00:10:42.080
You found a job

00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:43.510
as soon as you moved in.

00:10:43.790 --> 00:10:44.390
You're sure to be rolling

00:10:44.390 --> 00:10:45.790
in money in the future.

00:10:46.240 --> 00:10:46.870
Here's the thing,

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:47.630
the rent

00:10:47.630 --> 00:10:48.390
is usually

00:10:48.390 --> 00:10:49.600
paid annually.

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:51.440
I think you just came here

00:10:51.550 --> 00:10:53.000
and you said you'd
only stay for six months,

00:10:53.240 --> 00:10:54.480
plus you're so good at bargaining,

00:10:54.790 --> 00:10:55.240
so I let you

00:10:55.270 --> 00:10:56.910
pay only three months' rent.

00:10:57.270 --> 00:10:58.550
But I can't afford it.

00:10:58.630 --> 00:11:00.000
Could you pay me the annual rent?

00:11:00.750 --> 00:11:02.630
But we agreed on that.

00:11:03.910 --> 00:11:05.320
I'm a bit short

00:11:05.790 --> 00:11:07.360
on cash lately.

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:08.750
Pei, what's wrong?

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:10.240
It's all my bad luck.

00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:12.390
I'm losing money every day.

00:11:12.960 --> 00:11:14.030
My husband

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:15.150
will be angry

00:11:15.390 --> 00:11:16.390
if he finds out.

00:11:16.600 --> 00:11:18.390
Please pay me the annual rent

00:11:18.750 --> 00:11:19.840
so I can pay my debt.

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:20.670
Pei,

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:21.910
I did

00:11:21.960 --> 00:11:23.240
find a job before.

00:11:23.240 --> 00:11:24.840
But it was only short-term.

00:11:25.390 --> 00:11:26.750
If I pay you

00:11:26.750 --> 00:11:27.480
a year's rent,

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:29.030
what will I do if I can't

00:11:29.030 --> 00:11:29.840
find a job afterwards?

00:11:31.240 --> 00:11:33.080
You're so beautiful

00:11:33.080 --> 00:11:33.840
and smart.

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:34.670
How about this?

00:11:35.440 --> 00:11:36.440
You pay me the annual rent.

00:11:36.630 --> 00:11:38.120
I'll help you find a job.

00:11:38.630 --> 00:11:39.240
Pei.

00:11:39.870 --> 00:11:40.600
I can let you

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:41.960
use the fridge

00:11:41.960 --> 00:11:43.320
for free.

00:11:43.630 --> 00:11:44.030
Hey.

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:45.600
It's settled then.

00:11:45.790 --> 00:11:46.200
No.

00:11:46.270 --> 00:11:46.720
Pei...

00:11:46.910 --> 00:11:47.630
It's a promise!

00:11:56.600 --> 00:11:57.150
She's here.

00:11:58.870 --> 00:11:59.630
Hello.

00:12:00.320 --> 00:12:01.320
Li, right?

00:12:01.670 --> 00:12:02.320
I'm Zhang Li.

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:04.240
Call me Pei.

00:12:04.510 --> 00:12:05.720
The Pei Mei mentioned

00:12:05.790 --> 00:12:06.550
is me.

00:12:06.870 --> 00:12:07.840
Mei told me.

00:12:08.510 --> 00:12:09.550
That's great.

00:12:09.550 --> 00:12:11.750
Then we're friends.

00:12:12.150 --> 00:12:13.150
I'll call you Li.

00:12:13.150 --> 00:12:14.120
You can call me Pei.

00:12:14.270 --> 00:12:16.600
That way we don't need to be so formal.

00:12:17.150 --> 00:12:18.240
Mei was talking about her, right?

00:12:18.630 --> 00:12:19.240
Yes.

00:12:20.750 --> 00:12:22.870
Her name is Fang Wanzhi.

00:12:24.080 --> 00:12:24.870
Where are you from?

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:26.790
Guizhou.

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:28.120
How long have you been here?

00:12:28.790 --> 00:12:30.790
More than three years.

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:32.000
That's not short.

00:12:32.750 --> 00:12:34.000
Have you worked in a garment factory?

00:12:34.550 --> 00:12:35.480
She has.

00:12:35.550 --> 00:12:38.320
She's very skillful and
can do everything.

00:12:38.550 --> 00:12:39.320
I'm asking her.

00:12:41.630 --> 00:12:42.790
Okay.

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:48.150
I've been in Shenzhen for six months

00:12:48.790 --> 00:12:50.630
and haven't worked in a garment factory.

00:12:53.000 --> 00:12:54.750
But Pei wants to help me.

00:12:55.030 --> 00:12:55.600
Li,

00:12:55.670 --> 00:12:56.030
could you...?

00:12:56.030 --> 00:12:56.480
Stop.

00:13:00.270 --> 00:13:01.080
You seem

00:13:02.360 --> 00:13:03.270
quite honest.

00:13:04.360 --> 00:13:04.960
Come with me.

00:13:06.750 --> 00:13:07.550
Thank you, Li!

00:13:07.910 --> 00:13:08.840
Call me Ms. Zhang.

00:13:09.790 --> 00:13:10.600
Go.

00:13:11.480 --> 00:13:12.320
Ms. Zhang!

00:13:12.750 --> 00:13:14.240
Come have tea sometime!

00:13:14.750 --> 00:13:15.270
Ms. Zhang,

00:13:16.120 --> 00:13:16.670
thank you.

00:13:29.390 --> 00:13:30.000
A new girl has arrived.

00:13:30.150 --> 00:13:30.790
You can rest now.

00:13:31.480 --> 00:13:32.630
It's been 14 hours.

00:13:33.150 --> 00:13:33.870
I'll mark you as working overtime.

00:13:34.080 --> 00:13:34.750
Go to sleep.

00:13:36.550 --> 00:13:36.910
Come on,

00:13:37.200 --> 00:13:37.910
follow me.

00:13:40.720 --> 00:13:41.720
The travel rush is intense this year.

00:13:42.150 --> 00:13:43.440
Many girls want to come back

00:13:43.670 --> 00:13:44.510
but can't get tickets.

00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:46.200
We're short-staffed.

00:13:46.550 --> 00:13:47.510
Hope you can get up to speed quickly.

00:13:47.840 --> 00:13:48.270
Come on,

00:13:49.240 --> 00:13:50.630
we're currently making jeans.

00:13:51.390 --> 00:13:52.480
It's an order transferred
from Hong Kong.

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:53.390
Very urgent.

00:13:53.630 --> 00:13:54.790
We've specifically set up two lines.

00:13:55.840 --> 00:13:57.240
Do you know how to use an
electric sewing machine?

00:14:01.480 --> 00:14:02.240
Then see

00:14:02.480 --> 00:14:03.240
which one you can do.

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:04.550
Attach the back belt.

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:05.840
Hemming.

00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:06.870
Making buttonholes.

00:14:07.600 --> 00:14:08.240
Ironing?

00:14:08.480 --> 00:14:09.270
You know how to iron, right?

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:14.630
Sorry,

00:14:14.910 --> 00:14:15.910
do you have a canteen here?

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:17.550
I have experience helping
out in the kitchen.

00:14:18.030 --> 00:14:19.440
Hiring kitchen helpers
isn't my responsibility.

00:14:20.030 --> 00:14:20.910
If you don't want to work on the line,

00:14:21.480 --> 00:14:22.240
then leave.

00:14:22.510 --> 00:14:23.440
I want to.

00:14:24.270 --> 00:14:25.790
But I really don't know how.

00:14:29.320 --> 00:14:29.870
Then how about making buttons?

00:14:30.120 --> 00:14:30.750
Okay, making buttons.

00:14:31.030 --> 00:14:31.790
I'll teach you.

00:14:32.390 --> 00:14:33.390
You've come at the right time.

00:14:33.670 --> 00:14:34.630
We're desperately short-staffed.

00:14:35.320 --> 00:14:36.200
Thank you, Ms. Zhang.

00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:40.320
Go to work at station
number two in group one.

00:14:40.440 --> 00:14:40.960
Okay.

00:14:43.840 --> 00:14:45.030
Look, take two buttons.

00:14:45.080 --> 00:14:46.550
Put the smaller one at the bottom.

00:14:46.720 --> 00:14:47.670
Put the larger one on top.

00:14:47.870 --> 00:14:48.480
Step

00:14:49.150 --> 00:14:49.720
on this one.

00:14:50.030 --> 00:14:51.030
The button is now fastened.

00:14:54.550 --> 00:14:55.000
Four,

00:14:55.150 --> 00:14:56.000
what's your name again?

00:14:56.720 --> 00:14:57.360
Fang Wanzhi.

00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:58.750
Fill out the form.

00:14:58.910 --> 00:14:59.790
The requirements are strict now.

00:14:59.870 --> 00:15:00.910
Even if you only work one
day, you have to register.

00:15:03.870 --> 00:15:05.150
Come on. Sit here.

00:15:16.480 --> 00:15:17.390
You went to college?

00:15:18.840 --> 00:15:19.670
But I didn't graduate.

00:15:20.670 --> 00:15:21.600
That's good.

00:15:21.790 --> 00:15:22.630
Then I'm relieved.

00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:24.960
This job is for experienced workers.

00:15:25.720 --> 00:15:26.550
Not difficult for college graduates.

00:15:27.630 --> 00:15:28.790
I will try my best, Ms. Zhang.

00:15:29.390 --> 00:15:29.750
But I have

00:15:29.750 --> 00:15:31.000
to say this upfront.

00:15:32.270 --> 00:15:33.720
If you don't perform well enough

00:15:34.390 --> 00:15:35.630
for me or the director,

00:15:36.270 --> 00:15:37.120
you can be fired at any time.

00:15:41.120 --> 00:15:41.600
Ms. Zhang,

00:15:41.960 --> 00:15:42.630
since you're short-staffed,

00:15:42.630 --> 00:15:43.550
can I introduce one

00:15:43.550 --> 00:15:44.320
of my friends?

00:15:44.600 --> 00:15:45.750
She's very capable

00:15:45.910 --> 00:15:46.870
and has experience working

00:15:46.870 --> 00:15:47.670
in a garment factory.

00:15:47.910 --> 00:15:49.390
She'll be in Shenzhen in a few days.

00:15:50.390 --> 00:15:51.670
We'll see if you can stay here.

00:15:51.910 --> 00:15:52.510
Fill out the form.

00:15:58.600 --> 00:15:59.630
Ms. Zhang, I've finished.

00:16:00.630 --> 00:16:01.240
Start working.

00:16:11.270 --> 00:16:11.790
New girl!

00:16:12.480 --> 00:16:13.870
Don't blame me for not warning you.

00:16:14.270 --> 00:16:15.030
Ms. Zhang only gave you

00:16:15.030 --> 00:16:16.120
one day to practice.

00:16:16.550 --> 00:16:17.910
You'll officially start working
on the line tomorrow.

00:16:18.510 --> 00:16:19.000
If you

00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:20.150
delay the schedule,

00:16:20.630 --> 00:16:21.600
everyone of us

00:16:21.600 --> 00:16:22.270
will be dragged down.

00:16:23.510 --> 00:16:24.150
Got it.

00:16:26.840 --> 00:16:27.750
My name is Fang Wanzhi.

00:16:27.960 --> 00:16:28.750
What should I call you?

00:16:37.630 --> 00:16:38.670
Her name is Nan.

00:16:41.720 --> 00:16:42.320
Nan,

00:16:42.840 --> 00:16:44.390
that new girl went to college.

00:16:44.630 --> 00:16:45.550
Whatever.

00:16:45.870 --> 00:16:46.510
Whether she's a burden or not,

00:16:46.510 --> 00:16:47.320
we can't let her stay.

00:16:47.630 --> 00:16:48.150
Otherwise, where will

00:16:48.150 --> 00:16:48.910
our girls go when they come back?

00:17:13.750 --> 00:17:14.720
Lunch time!

00:17:15.160 --> 00:17:16.000
I'll practice a little longer.

00:17:16.350 --> 00:17:17.070
Lunch break is only ten minutes.

00:17:17.070 --> 00:17:18.200
If you're late, there
won't be any food left!

00:17:18.510 --> 00:17:19.110
Thanks!

00:17:45.270 --> 00:17:46.200
I almost forgot about you.

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:48.550
You haven't eaten yet.

00:18:01.920 --> 00:18:03.000
I'll go out and buy something,

00:18:03.270 --> 00:18:04.640
then we'll both have something to eat.

00:18:22.070 --> 00:18:22.880
Nan, good morning.

00:18:41.240 --> 00:18:41.790
Li!

00:18:43.310 --> 00:18:43.880
You're back.

00:18:44.160 --> 00:18:44.550
Come on,

00:18:44.960 --> 00:18:45.640
go help her.

00:18:46.830 --> 00:18:47.640
Tidy this up.

00:18:47.920 --> 00:18:50.030
You go open buttonholes.

00:18:52.680 --> 00:18:53.270
The girls

00:18:53.270 --> 00:18:54.640
are gradually returning.

00:18:54.680 --> 00:18:55.400
Those who aren't skilled

00:18:55.480 --> 00:18:56.550
shouldn't take up space.

00:19:12.960 --> 00:19:13.790
Girls!

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:14.550
Stop for a second!

00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:15.310
Listen.

00:19:16.240 --> 00:19:17.070
This batch is urgent.

00:19:17.160 --> 00:19:18.200
The assembly line can't stop.

00:19:18.400 --> 00:19:19.960
Even-numbered girls eat first.

00:19:20.240 --> 00:19:21.480
Odd-numbered girls eat at 12.

00:19:21.720 --> 00:19:22.400
Wait for the next bell.

00:19:45.510 --> 00:19:46.400
Lunchtime!

00:19:46.880 --> 00:19:47.640
I'm even-numbered.

00:19:48.640 --> 00:19:49.960
You didn't go.

00:19:50.240 --> 00:19:50.830
I'm not hungry.

00:20:18.480 --> 00:20:19.790
You haven't been to the bathroom?

00:20:21.510 --> 00:20:22.720
I haven't drunk water all day

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:23.920
so I wouldn't need to go to the toilet.

00:20:27.070 --> 00:20:27.960
What should I call you?

00:20:29.550 --> 00:20:30.440
Call me Three.

00:20:40.270 --> 00:20:40.960
Stop. Stop.

00:20:41.440 --> 00:20:42.110
Stop!

00:20:43.830 --> 00:20:44.510
What happened?

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:46.590
We've fallen so far this morning.

00:20:46.830 --> 00:20:47.920
We're going to lose the order!

00:20:48.110 --> 00:20:49.240
Ms. Zhang,

00:20:49.350 --> 00:20:51.000
it's not our fault.

00:20:51.270 --> 00:20:52.920
You should ask Four.

00:20:54.550 --> 00:20:55.590
What did I do?

00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:57.880
You haven't even
finished half of your work

00:20:57.960 --> 00:20:58.880
and you're still chatting.

00:20:59.000 --> 00:21:00.110
What do you think?

00:21:00.310 --> 00:21:02.000
You're dragging us down.

00:21:02.000 --> 00:21:02.750
Yeah.

00:21:02.790 --> 00:21:03.790
We can't sew the leather labels

00:21:03.790 --> 00:21:04.830
before attaching the buttons.

00:21:08.310 --> 00:21:09.270
Ms. Zhang, I'm sorry.

00:21:09.880 --> 00:21:10.880
I'll practice more.

00:21:11.640 --> 00:21:12.640
It'll be too late

00:21:12.830 --> 00:21:14.270
by the time she gets used to it.

00:21:14.400 --> 00:21:15.030
Ms. Zhang,

00:21:15.510 --> 00:21:17.440
Wei and He will arrive in two days.

00:21:17.720 --> 00:21:19.830
They're much more capable than her.

00:21:25.110 --> 00:21:25.640
Four.

00:21:27.790 --> 00:21:28.440
It seems you're really

00:21:28.440 --> 00:21:29.160
not cut out for this.

00:21:29.550 --> 00:21:30.310
Go collect your paycheck.

00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:31.550
Ms. Zhang.

00:21:32.510 --> 00:21:33.440
I want to try again.

00:21:33.720 --> 00:21:34.550
I'm sure I can do it.

00:21:35.200 --> 00:21:36.790
It's not up to you.

00:21:37.790 --> 00:21:38.880
There are many girls in the factory.

00:21:39.160 --> 00:21:40.070
Once they all come back,

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:41.550
you'll still be laid off.

00:21:42.830 --> 00:21:44.270
If I still can't do it by then,

00:21:44.270 --> 00:21:45.480
I'll leave.

00:21:45.720 --> 00:21:47.160
But please give me another chance.

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:49.000
I promise I can sew buttons

00:21:49.160 --> 00:21:50.590
faster than you within three days.

00:21:51.400 --> 00:21:52.880
She promises?

00:21:53.070 --> 00:21:54.240
She's too

00:21:54.310 --> 00:21:55.720
confident.

00:21:57.510 --> 00:21:58.110
Ms. Zhang.

00:21:58.790 --> 00:21:59.350
Ms. Zhang.

00:22:01.070 --> 00:22:02.750
Please give Four another chance.

00:22:04.070 --> 00:22:04.960
She hasn't

00:22:05.070 --> 00:22:06.750
eaten lunch for two days.

00:22:07.350 --> 00:22:08.550
She hasn't drunk water

00:22:08.680 --> 00:22:10.030
to not use the bathroom.

00:22:12.440 --> 00:22:13.880
So what if she doesn't eat or drink?

00:22:14.240 --> 00:22:15.440
She's still a burden to us.

00:22:18.920 --> 00:22:19.790
Come with me.

00:22:25.270 --> 00:22:26.270
You really haven't drunk any water?

00:22:28.070 --> 00:22:28.550
No.

00:22:29.200 --> 00:22:30.310
Being stubborn won't help.

00:22:30.960 --> 00:22:31.510
I knew you couldn't do it

00:22:31.510 --> 00:22:32.590
the moment I saw you.

00:22:33.030 --> 00:22:34.310
You must have been spoiled growing up.

00:22:34.920 --> 00:22:36.790
You're college-educated and pretty.

00:22:37.200 --> 00:22:38.440
You could find a better job.

00:22:38.960 --> 00:22:39.960
Why suffer here?

00:22:41.680 --> 00:22:42.960
I don't want to fail so easily.

00:22:46.070 --> 00:22:47.640
Ms. Zhang, please give
me another chance.

00:22:51.160 --> 00:22:51.920
Go to the bathroom.

00:22:53.160 --> 00:22:53.830
Drink enough water.

00:22:54.200 --> 00:22:54.880
Take a ten-minute break.

00:22:57.830 --> 00:22:58.550
Thank you, Ms. Zhang.

00:23:45.680 --> 00:23:46.590
Sir, wait!

00:23:46.720 --> 00:23:47.400
I'm getting my luggage.

00:23:49.720 --> 00:23:50.550
It's a bit heavy.

00:23:52.590 --> 00:23:53.070
Come on.

00:23:58.680 --> 00:23:59.960
You're finally back.

00:24:00.510 --> 00:24:02.350
I couldn't have held on any longer.

00:24:02.920 --> 00:24:04.480
Good for you.

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:05.960
You've even found a job.

00:24:06.480 --> 00:24:07.790
I could be fired at any moment.

00:24:08.310 --> 00:24:09.350
I'm so stupid.

00:24:10.000 --> 00:24:11.270
You're stupid?

00:24:11.640 --> 00:24:12.640
No way.

00:24:13.240 --> 00:24:14.160
This kind of work

00:24:14.160 --> 00:24:15.750
is all about practice making perfect.

00:24:15.790 --> 00:24:16.310
You know?

00:24:16.880 --> 00:24:18.030
You can definitely do it.

00:24:18.200 --> 00:24:18.640
I'll take you to see Ms. Zhang

00:24:18.640 --> 00:24:19.640
first thing tomorrow morning.

00:24:22.110 --> 00:24:23.070
The bus is here! Come on.

00:24:27.350 --> 00:24:28.200
Wanzhi,

00:24:28.680 --> 00:24:29.830
you've decorated this house

00:24:29.830 --> 00:24:31.350
so beautifully.

00:24:32.550 --> 00:24:33.030
How is it?

00:24:33.640 --> 00:24:34.240
Is it good?

00:24:35.400 --> 00:24:35.830
Yes.

00:24:35.960 --> 00:24:36.720
It's really good.

00:24:37.550 --> 00:24:38.640
It's just too oily.

00:24:38.750 --> 00:24:40.070
Pancakes with braised pork

00:24:40.070 --> 00:24:41.350
are bound to be oily.

00:24:41.640 --> 00:24:43.110
My mom specifically asked
me to bring you this.

00:24:43.510 --> 00:24:44.480
Thanks.

00:24:44.880 --> 00:24:45.720
Your mom's cooking is great.

00:24:46.110 --> 00:24:47.720
I think you're craving meat.

00:24:50.350 --> 00:24:50.960
Okay.

00:24:51.510 --> 00:24:53.070
Little Friend is craving meat.

00:24:53.680 --> 00:24:55.640
I've been too busy lately to feed her.

00:24:57.590 --> 00:24:58.440
Try this.

00:24:58.440 --> 00:25:00.070
Come on, try it.

00:25:04.510 --> 00:25:05.640
Is it good?

00:25:19.720 --> 00:25:20.960
Why is that woman glaring at you?

00:25:23.720 --> 00:25:25.030
We're on the same line.

00:25:25.400 --> 00:25:26.240
A few of her friends

00:25:26.240 --> 00:25:26.960
haven't come back yet.

00:25:27.000 --> 00:25:28.160
She's afraid I'll take their place,

00:25:28.310 --> 00:25:29.590
so she's been ostracizing me.

00:25:32.550 --> 00:25:33.270
What line?

00:25:34.590 --> 00:25:36.000
It's the assembly line.

00:25:36.440 --> 00:25:37.550
Also, the production line.

00:25:37.720 --> 00:25:38.720
It's called "line"

00:25:38.720 --> 00:25:39.590
for short.

00:25:39.960 --> 00:25:40.750
Ms. Zhang, whom we're

00:25:40.750 --> 00:25:41.640
meeting later,

00:25:41.880 --> 00:25:42.640
is in charge

00:25:42.640 --> 00:25:43.640
of the assembly line.

00:25:45.310 --> 00:25:45.880
I see.

00:25:48.350 --> 00:25:49.110
Ms. Zhang!

00:25:49.480 --> 00:25:50.440
She's the Li Juan

00:25:50.440 --> 00:25:51.270
I told you about.

00:25:52.880 --> 00:25:53.720
You're not even sure

00:25:53.720 --> 00:25:54.480
if you can stay,

00:25:54.640 --> 00:25:55.480
yet you're recommending her.

00:25:56.550 --> 00:25:57.720
She'll definitely be fine.

00:25:59.350 --> 00:26:00.200
I used to be a tailor.

00:26:01.310 --> 00:26:03.270
You look like you know how to work.

00:26:04.790 --> 00:26:06.440
Most of the girls have returned.

00:26:06.750 --> 00:26:07.880
There are limited openings.

00:26:08.510 --> 00:26:09.720
Aren't you afraid

00:26:09.830 --> 00:26:10.510
you'll be fired

00:26:10.920 --> 00:26:11.590
if she stays?

00:26:14.110 --> 00:26:14.680
It's okay.

00:26:14.790 --> 00:26:15.880
She's my best friend.

00:26:16.030 --> 00:26:16.510
No.

00:26:16.680 --> 00:26:18.070
Either Wanzhi and I stay

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:19.160
or we both leave.

00:26:21.240 --> 00:26:22.310
She's holding the girls back.

00:26:22.440 --> 00:26:23.510
Everyone has a problem with her.

00:26:24.160 --> 00:26:26.350
You think you can do
the work of two people?

00:26:26.680 --> 00:26:27.440
I'll give it a try.

00:26:55.680 --> 00:26:56.270
Ms. Zhang,

00:26:56.880 --> 00:26:58.350
another new girl?

00:26:58.750 --> 00:26:59.590
Wei and He will

00:26:59.590 --> 00:27:00.640
arrive tomorrow morning.

00:27:02.000 --> 00:27:03.590
When we had the most orders,

00:27:03.830 --> 00:27:05.030
Wei insisted on going home

00:27:05.440 --> 00:27:06.790
ten days early.

00:27:07.270 --> 00:27:07.920
He had the most

00:27:07.920 --> 00:27:09.200
unexcused absences

00:27:09.350 --> 00:27:10.400
in the entire workshop last year.

00:27:11.110 --> 00:27:12.110
Don't you know that?

00:27:12.680 --> 00:27:13.350
Besides,

00:27:13.550 --> 00:27:14.510
not everyone on this line

00:27:15.030 --> 00:27:16.070
should be your girl.

00:27:17.200 --> 00:27:18.070
Do your job well.

00:27:20.480 --> 00:27:21.590
Li Juan. Fang Wanzhi.

00:27:22.270 --> 00:27:23.750
Come find me after work.

00:27:24.350 --> 00:27:25.240
Let's sign formal contracts.

00:27:38.830 --> 00:27:39.510
This food

00:27:40.240 --> 00:27:41.270
is far worse than the canteen

00:27:41.270 --> 00:27:42.310
at our construction site.

00:27:42.680 --> 00:27:43.550
Yes.

00:27:43.960 --> 00:27:45.830
I'm craving Liu Zhu's noodles.

00:27:48.240 --> 00:27:49.350
Li Juan, you're amazing.

00:27:49.680 --> 00:27:50.350
You're number one

00:27:50.350 --> 00:27:51.920
on the line right away.

00:27:52.200 --> 00:27:53.240
Who said that?

00:27:53.400 --> 00:27:54.510
I can tell.

00:27:56.680 --> 00:27:57.750
I've loved sewing

00:27:57.750 --> 00:27:59.000
and mending since I was little.

00:27:59.310 --> 00:27:59.960
I even made

00:27:59.960 --> 00:28:01.480
clothes for my siblings.

00:28:01.750 --> 00:28:02.750
Then I learned tailoring

00:28:02.750 --> 00:28:03.880
from my aunt for two years.

00:28:05.440 --> 00:28:06.030
No wonder.

00:28:06.920 --> 00:28:07.350
Come on.

00:28:10.110 --> 00:28:10.510
Yeah.

00:28:18.680 --> 00:28:20.240
According to Ms. Zhang,

00:28:20.400 --> 00:28:22.160
Wei and He are not coming back?

00:28:23.030 --> 00:28:23.680
She's just afraid

00:28:23.680 --> 00:28:24.830
we'll unite

00:28:25.070 --> 00:28:25.830
and not listen to her.

00:28:26.240 --> 00:28:27.310
What should we do then?

00:28:27.830 --> 00:28:28.680
Will she

00:28:29.350 --> 00:28:32.590
make things difficult for us?

00:28:32.920 --> 00:28:33.640
She wouldn't dare.

00:28:35.240 --> 00:28:35.790
Nan,

00:28:36.160 --> 00:28:38.030
if you can't protect us,

00:28:38.590 --> 00:28:40.680
who will listen to you in the future?

00:28:55.720 --> 00:28:56.680
I remember you said

00:28:57.160 --> 00:28:58.070
you'd surpass me in three days.

00:29:01.070 --> 00:29:02.550
I was too eager

00:29:02.550 --> 00:29:03.750
and boasted that day.

00:29:04.400 --> 00:29:05.160
For a beginner,

00:29:05.270 --> 00:29:06.510
this is quite good.

00:29:08.750 --> 00:29:09.920
Ms. Zhang.

00:29:10.640 --> 00:29:12.160
She's always making buttonholes.

00:29:12.270 --> 00:29:14.310
That's the easiest job.

00:29:14.400 --> 00:29:15.830
It's not fair.

00:29:16.400 --> 00:29:17.400
I can learn anything.

00:29:18.030 --> 00:29:19.270
Master this first.

00:29:19.750 --> 00:29:20.510
I'm the boss here.

00:29:20.920 --> 00:29:21.960
You don't need to care what others say.

00:29:26.960 --> 00:29:28.350
Fang Wanzhi, you've changed.

00:29:28.960 --> 00:29:29.830
How have I changed?

00:29:30.680 --> 00:29:31.680
You've become weak.

00:29:32.350 --> 00:29:33.310
You weren't like this

00:29:33.310 --> 00:29:34.160
when Hao Qianqian bullied you

00:29:34.160 --> 00:29:35.000
at the canteen.

00:29:36.070 --> 00:29:37.110
It was different.

00:29:37.310 --> 00:29:38.880
Hao Qianqian was picking on me.

00:29:39.590 --> 00:29:41.200
Now I'm just not capable enough.

00:29:42.350 --> 00:29:43.440
To be honest,

00:29:44.440 --> 00:29:45.160
this kind of work

00:29:45.160 --> 00:29:46.350
isn't really suitable for you.

00:29:46.880 --> 00:29:48.790
After all, you're the
Princess of Yu County.

00:29:50.000 --> 00:29:51.000
What Princess of Yu County?

00:29:51.000 --> 00:29:51.960
You're mocking me.

00:29:53.310 --> 00:29:54.070
That's the most

00:29:54.070 --> 00:29:55.440
embarrassing thing for me.

00:29:56.310 --> 00:29:57.400
I shouldn't have told you.

00:29:57.550 --> 00:29:59.200
What? Are you angry?

00:29:59.550 --> 00:30:00.510
I'm sorry.

00:30:00.920 --> 00:30:01.960
Even if you're not a princess,

00:30:01.960 --> 00:30:02.590
you don't have

00:30:02.590 --> 00:30:03.790
to be so humble.

00:30:06.200 --> 00:30:07.550
Am I being humble?

00:30:08.680 --> 00:30:09.720
Before, even though

00:30:10.510 --> 00:30:11.110
we were washing vegetables

00:30:11.110 --> 00:30:12.350
and dishes at the construction site,

00:30:13.030 --> 00:30:13.720
you always had

00:30:13.720 --> 00:30:15.310
that arrogance on your face.

00:30:16.750 --> 00:30:17.920
But it's gone now.

00:30:20.000 --> 00:30:20.960
I've never had

00:30:20.960 --> 00:30:22.030
that arrogance on me.

00:30:22.350 --> 00:30:23.750
But I really like it.

00:30:30.070 --> 00:30:31.400
I think I understand what you mean.

00:30:47.640 --> 00:30:49.110
That's right.

00:30:49.200 --> 00:30:50.510
Why should we be afraid of her?

00:30:53.310 --> 00:30:54.030
Nan,

00:30:54.440 --> 00:30:55.880
she is provoking you.

00:30:56.880 --> 00:30:58.350
She's arrogant just because

00:30:58.830 --> 00:30:59.960
Ms. Zhang is backing her up.

00:31:01.350 --> 00:31:02.510
She'll regret it.

00:31:14.550 --> 00:31:15.440
Let's work harder this afternoon,

00:31:15.720 --> 00:31:17.240
and we can finish this batch of orders.

00:31:17.510 --> 00:31:18.350
Thanks for your hard work.

00:31:18.750 --> 00:31:21.350
Mr. Huang said tomorrow is a day off!

00:31:21.720 --> 00:31:23.510
Yay!

00:31:38.750 --> 00:31:39.350
Three.

00:31:42.160 --> 00:31:42.960
Why aren't you happy

00:31:42.960 --> 00:31:44.160
about a day off tomorrow?

00:31:45.110 --> 00:31:45.720
Happy?

00:31:46.310 --> 00:31:47.680
A day off means one less day's pay.

00:31:48.200 --> 00:31:49.200
What's there to be happy about?

00:31:50.070 --> 00:31:51.350
We can't work all the time.

00:31:51.440 --> 00:31:52.350
We need to rest.

00:31:55.110 --> 00:31:56.070
If you're free tomorrow,

00:31:56.160 --> 00:31:57.350
let's go shopping together.

00:31:59.750 --> 00:32:00.830
No, thank you.

00:32:09.830 --> 00:32:11.070
What's wrong with Three?

00:32:13.110 --> 00:32:14.350
It's not her fault.

00:32:17.750 --> 00:32:18.400
I see.

00:32:18.920 --> 00:32:20.440
She's afraid of being ostracized by Nan

00:32:20.480 --> 00:32:21.440
if she gets too close to us.

00:32:22.240 --> 00:32:23.350
Nan's girls

00:32:23.550 --> 00:32:24.510
are either her relatives

00:32:24.510 --> 00:32:25.310
or from her hometown.

00:32:25.350 --> 00:32:26.310
Only Three isn't.

00:32:27.160 --> 00:32:28.400
By the way, I asked her.

00:32:29.270 --> 00:32:30.880
She seems to be from your hometown.

00:32:31.720 --> 00:32:32.270
Really?

00:32:33.510 --> 00:32:34.640
Our province is quite big, then.

00:32:34.790 --> 00:32:35.440
No.

00:32:35.880 --> 00:32:37.110
She's from Yu County.

00:32:37.590 --> 00:32:38.310
Really?

00:32:41.830 --> 00:32:42.680
Three!

00:32:43.350 --> 00:32:44.720
I heard you're also from Yu County.

00:32:45.350 --> 00:32:46.200
Which part of Yu County?

00:32:47.750 --> 00:32:48.750
Shenshan Valley.

00:32:49.030 --> 00:32:50.510
You wouldn't know anyway.

00:32:51.750 --> 00:32:52.310
Three!

00:32:53.640 --> 00:32:54.790
I'm also from Shenshan Valley.

00:32:55.070 --> 00:32:55.790
Have you heard

00:32:56.440 --> 00:32:57.200
of Shenxian Peak?

00:32:58.790 --> 00:32:59.350
No.

00:33:02.480 --> 00:33:02.880
Come on.

00:33:03.720 --> 00:33:04.790
When I first arrived,

00:33:05.110 --> 00:33:06.030
Three even

00:33:06.030 --> 00:33:07.480
spoke up for me.

00:33:07.750 --> 00:33:08.510
Why now...?

00:33:11.030 --> 00:33:12.750
Don't you understand?

00:33:13.790 --> 00:33:15.200
She's just trying to survive.

00:33:16.070 --> 00:33:16.920
She has no

00:33:17.070 --> 00:33:18.750
connections or friends.

00:33:19.030 --> 00:33:20.000
Getting this job

00:33:20.000 --> 00:33:21.200
must have been tough.

00:33:22.400 --> 00:33:23.000
Fine then.

00:33:23.200 --> 00:33:24.680
I won't talk to her anymore,

00:33:24.880 --> 00:33:26.000
so as not to implicate her.

00:33:27.960 --> 00:33:29.270
Let's eat out tomorrow.

00:33:30.240 --> 00:33:31.160
Okay.

00:33:31.680 --> 00:33:33.550
The food in the factory is so bland.

00:33:33.550 --> 00:33:34.550
I'm craving meat.

00:33:35.160 --> 00:33:36.070
I also want to treat someone else.

00:33:36.510 --> 00:33:37.110
Who?

00:33:38.310 --> 00:33:39.750
I want to treat people
who have helped us.

00:33:39.750 --> 00:33:40.920
Like Gao Xiang.

00:33:41.030 --> 00:33:41.400
And...

00:33:41.400 --> 00:33:41.830
What? You...

00:33:42.000 --> 00:33:43.400
Why do you want to treat him?

00:33:43.590 --> 00:33:44.830
He did help us.

00:33:44.830 --> 00:33:46.240
And more than once.

00:33:46.960 --> 00:33:48.240
I don't really like him.

00:33:49.160 --> 00:33:49.750
Fine.

00:33:50.000 --> 00:33:50.720
You don't like him.

00:33:50.720 --> 00:33:51.640
Then I won't treat him.

00:33:53.550 --> 00:33:54.640
I also want to treat Li.

00:33:55.720 --> 00:33:56.240
Li?

00:33:56.960 --> 00:33:57.880
Ms. Zhang.

00:33:57.880 --> 00:33:59.270
She told me to call her that.

00:34:00.070 --> 00:34:01.830
She's really been very good to you.

00:34:02.240 --> 00:34:03.270
We've benefited a lot

00:34:03.270 --> 00:34:04.310
from her help at the factory.

00:34:04.350 --> 00:34:05.000
We should thank her.

00:34:05.310 --> 00:34:05.830
Okay.

00:34:10.280 --> 00:34:12.070
You didn't need to order
such expensive seafood.

00:34:12.710 --> 00:34:13.800
You work hard for your money.

00:34:14.000 --> 00:34:14.840
Be careful with your spending.

00:34:15.400 --> 00:34:17.320
It's kind of you to come.

00:34:17.550 --> 00:34:18.550
Li Juan invited me.

00:34:18.710 --> 00:34:19.920
Of course I had to come.

00:34:25.630 --> 00:34:27.110
Even though you introduced her to me,

00:34:27.360 --> 00:34:28.440
I liked her the moment

00:34:28.670 --> 00:34:29.320
I saw her.

00:34:30.590 --> 00:34:31.800
Don't take offense at my words.

00:34:32.280 --> 00:34:33.280
It's like a teacher

00:34:33.280 --> 00:34:34.710
liking a good student.

00:34:34.920 --> 00:34:35.920
I just like girls

00:34:36.150 --> 00:34:37.710
who can do the work.

00:34:39.070 --> 00:34:40.400
Of course not.

00:34:41.030 --> 00:34:41.590
I'm happy

00:34:41.760 --> 00:34:42.670
for Li Juan.

00:34:43.030 --> 00:34:43.630
Li,

00:34:44.360 --> 00:34:45.590
Wanzhi went to university.

00:34:45.670 --> 00:34:47.320
Her strengths aren't in the workshop.

00:34:47.360 --> 00:34:48.280
I know.

00:34:48.510 --> 00:34:49.920
But I'm in charge of the workshop.

00:34:50.280 --> 00:34:50.710
I don't see

00:34:51.190 --> 00:34:51.880
any other strengths

00:34:51.880 --> 00:34:53.030
in her.

00:34:53.710 --> 00:34:55.400
Li, Wanzhi and I

00:34:55.510 --> 00:34:56.150
have been very grateful

00:34:56.150 --> 00:34:57.280
for your help these past few months.

00:34:57.480 --> 00:34:58.590
We'd like to toast you.

00:34:59.670 --> 00:35:00.230
Wait for a second.

00:35:01.070 --> 00:35:02.840
I have something to say.

00:35:03.630 --> 00:35:04.440
Mr. Huang

00:35:04.760 --> 00:35:05.630
talked to me.

00:35:05.920 --> 00:35:07.070
He said there are some slackers

00:35:07.710 --> 00:35:08.760
in the workshop

00:35:09.030 --> 00:35:09.960
and I need to fire them.

00:35:11.710 --> 00:35:12.400
Me?

00:35:12.510 --> 00:35:13.510
I can't think

00:35:13.550 --> 00:35:14.760
of anyone else but you.

00:35:15.670 --> 00:35:16.710
But if I had to,

00:35:17.030 --> 00:35:18.030
Three would count.

00:35:18.510 --> 00:35:19.590
Three?

00:35:20.150 --> 00:35:21.670
She's better than me.

00:35:22.000 --> 00:35:23.280
And she came earlier than me.

00:35:23.320 --> 00:35:24.360
Not too early.

00:35:24.960 --> 00:35:26.000
It was around the New Year

00:35:26.110 --> 00:35:27.320
when the factory was most short-staffed.

00:35:27.710 --> 00:35:29.400
She was waiting at the factory gate.

00:35:29.630 --> 00:35:30.510
So I hired her.

00:35:31.880 --> 00:35:34.030
If I had to fire one of you,

00:35:34.880 --> 00:35:36.070
who do you think

00:35:36.760 --> 00:35:37.760
I should fire?

00:35:42.110 --> 00:35:42.630
Ms. Zhang.

00:35:42.670 --> 00:35:44.280
Please give Four another chance.

00:35:44.840 --> 00:35:45.710
She hasn't

00:35:45.880 --> 00:35:47.480
eaten lunch for two days.

00:35:47.840 --> 00:35:49.000
She hasn't drunk water

00:35:49.150 --> 00:35:50.480
to not use the bathroom.

00:35:56.630 --> 00:35:57.510
I won't make things difficult for you.

00:35:58.150 --> 00:35:58.800
To tell you the truth,

00:35:59.150 --> 00:36:00.840
I refused.

00:36:01.360 --> 00:36:02.150
I won't fire either of you.

00:36:02.550 --> 00:36:03.190
You two

00:36:03.190 --> 00:36:04.320
are doing your jobs well.

00:36:04.510 --> 00:36:05.510
Why would I fire you?

00:36:07.110 --> 00:36:08.880
I'm telling you,

00:36:09.000 --> 00:36:10.480
someone's been badmouthing.

00:36:10.800 --> 00:36:11.590
She just wants

00:36:11.590 --> 00:36:12.760
to replace the entire line

00:36:13.070 --> 00:36:14.510
with her people.

00:36:15.840 --> 00:36:17.480
I won't let her succeed.

00:36:18.630 --> 00:36:19.480
Thanks, Li.

00:36:19.510 --> 00:36:20.280
We should drink for this.

00:36:21.030 --> 00:36:22.110
Wait. There's something else.

00:36:26.110 --> 00:36:27.400
It's good news.

00:36:29.590 --> 00:36:30.710
Mr. Huang talked to me

00:36:30.920 --> 00:36:31.510
about promoting

00:36:32.000 --> 00:36:33.150
an assistant head.

00:36:33.510 --> 00:36:34.190
I want

00:36:35.880 --> 00:36:36.480
to nominate Li Juan.

00:36:38.920 --> 00:36:39.710
What?

00:36:40.510 --> 00:36:41.550
You think you're not good enough?

00:36:41.880 --> 00:36:43.400
Is my judgment

00:36:43.550 --> 00:36:44.360
flawed?

00:36:44.590 --> 00:36:45.550
Not at all.

00:36:45.840 --> 00:36:46.590
Li, your judgment

00:36:46.590 --> 00:36:47.710
is not flawed.

00:36:47.960 --> 00:36:49.230
Li Juan is capable.

00:36:49.440 --> 00:36:50.880
She's the best on the whole line.

00:36:51.400 --> 00:36:52.030
When did I tell you

00:36:52.030 --> 00:36:53.190
to call me Li?

00:36:54.960 --> 00:36:55.480
Li Juan,

00:36:56.320 --> 00:36:56.960
tell me.

00:36:57.440 --> 00:36:58.000
Do you dare

00:36:58.320 --> 00:36:58.960
to be the assistant head?

00:37:01.480 --> 00:37:02.110
Yes.

00:37:02.710 --> 00:37:03.960
And I'm sure I can do it well.

00:37:04.840 --> 00:37:05.840
Ms. Zhang, thanks for your trust.

00:37:06.030 --> 00:37:06.590
Call me Li.

00:37:06.880 --> 00:37:07.400
Li!

00:37:07.840 --> 00:37:08.710
That's more like it.

00:37:08.840 --> 00:37:09.230
Come on.

00:37:09.510 --> 00:37:10.070
Cheers!

00:37:10.800 --> 00:37:11.400
Cheers!

00:37:20.880 --> 00:37:22.440
Li is straightforward.

00:37:22.630 --> 00:37:23.840
Don't mind her.

00:37:25.550 --> 00:37:27.360
It's my own incompetence.

00:37:27.840 --> 00:37:28.880
She didn't

00:37:29.190 --> 00:37:30.440
fire me

00:37:30.440 --> 00:37:31.630
because of you.

00:37:31.960 --> 00:37:33.800
I'll need your help from now on.

00:37:35.000 --> 00:37:36.360
If I become the assistant head,

00:37:36.590 --> 00:37:38.110
I really won't be able to
look after you anymore.

00:37:38.280 --> 00:37:39.190
There are over 20 girls

00:37:39.190 --> 00:37:40.110
on one line.

00:37:40.280 --> 00:37:41.440
Everyone can see who's

00:37:41.440 --> 00:37:42.840
doing well and who's not.

00:37:43.510 --> 00:37:44.880
Wow, Li Juan.

00:37:45.110 --> 00:37:46.480
So you're going to turn
your back on me already?

00:37:46.710 --> 00:37:48.110
That's not what I meant.

00:37:48.510 --> 00:37:49.320
I'm mad.

00:37:50.440 --> 00:37:51.280
Are you really angry?

00:37:56.630 --> 00:37:57.440
Then I won't

00:37:58.590 --> 00:38:00.070
be the assistant head.

00:38:03.110 --> 00:38:03.840
Really?

00:38:08.230 --> 00:38:09.000
I was just teasing you.

00:38:09.000 --> 00:38:10.590
Can't you see?

00:38:12.230 --> 00:38:13.480
Becoming the assistant head

00:38:13.590 --> 00:38:14.630
is a milestone for working

00:38:14.630 --> 00:38:15.630
in Shenzhen.

00:38:15.840 --> 00:38:17.480
I'm happy for you.

00:38:19.840 --> 00:38:23.590
My friend is going to be a leader!

00:38:24.280 --> 00:38:27.440
Even working girls have their day!

00:38:27.440 --> 00:38:28.400
Alright,

00:38:28.630 --> 00:38:29.670
stop yelling.

00:38:35.230 --> 00:38:36.550
Mr. Huang is here!

00:38:37.320 --> 00:38:38.320
Come on, stop for a moment.

00:38:38.440 --> 00:38:39.550
Girls, stop for a second.

00:38:40.320 --> 00:38:42.000
Mr. Huang has come to visit us.

00:38:42.320 --> 00:38:44.030
Let's invite Mr. Huang to speak.

00:38:49.150 --> 00:38:50.190
Thanks to everyone,

00:38:51.190 --> 00:38:52.150
our factory

00:38:52.630 --> 00:38:53.920
received large orders

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:54.960
before the New Year.

00:38:55.480 --> 00:38:57.550
From March to June,

00:38:57.550 --> 00:38:58.280
we received

00:38:58.480 --> 00:39:00.000
several large orders.

00:39:00.440 --> 00:39:01.550
Thanks to the hard work

00:39:01.590 --> 00:39:02.670
of all the ladies,

00:39:03.110 --> 00:39:04.920
we completed the orders on time

00:39:05.070 --> 00:39:06.000
and with high quality.

00:39:06.280 --> 00:39:07.360
The clients were very satisfied.

00:39:08.510 --> 00:39:09.190
I am

00:39:09.630 --> 00:39:11.630
deeply grateful.

00:39:16.960 --> 00:39:18.590
There's more good news.

00:39:19.030 --> 00:39:19.920
Our factory is about

00:39:20.550 --> 00:39:22.190
to experience the most

00:39:22.510 --> 00:39:23.880
glorious moment since opening.

00:39:24.230 --> 00:39:25.150
We received a super order

00:39:25.230 --> 00:39:26.590
for Fire Phoenix denim

00:39:27.150 --> 00:39:28.760
clothing production

00:39:28.920 --> 00:39:30.590
and processing!

00:39:31.230 --> 00:39:32.480
Fire Phoenix?

00:39:32.800 --> 00:39:34.320
That's a famous brand!

00:39:34.440 --> 00:39:34.800
Yes,

00:39:35.030 --> 00:39:36.230
it's very famous.

00:39:36.630 --> 00:39:37.960
Securing this order

00:39:38.190 --> 00:39:39.150
was really not easy.

00:39:39.760 --> 00:39:40.920
So I hope you

00:39:41.440 --> 00:39:43.070
can help me

00:39:43.760 --> 00:39:44.760
complete this order.

00:39:45.230 --> 00:39:46.670
With the support of the famous brand,

00:39:47.230 --> 00:39:48.670
our factory will continue to thrive.

00:39:49.360 --> 00:39:51.030
I make a promise here.

00:39:51.190 --> 00:39:53.480
After successfully completing this,

00:39:54.190 --> 00:39:55.630
I will give everyone

00:39:56.000 --> 00:39:57.440
a bonus!

00:39:59.150 --> 00:40:00.070
Yay!

00:40:05.760 --> 00:40:07.070
But I can't just say nice things.

00:40:07.510 --> 00:40:08.960
So listen.

00:40:09.440 --> 00:40:10.590
If anyone delays

00:40:10.670 --> 00:40:11.630
the schedule

00:40:12.320 --> 00:40:14.030
or causes quality issues

00:40:14.510 --> 00:40:15.760
due to carelessness,

00:40:16.320 --> 00:40:18.590
resulting in the orders not
being completed on time,

00:40:18.960 --> 00:40:19.710
they will be fired immediately.

00:40:20.480 --> 00:40:21.110
No hesitation.

00:40:22.360 --> 00:40:22.960
Ms. Zhang,

00:40:23.230 --> 00:40:24.030
your turn.

00:40:24.920 --> 00:40:25.760
I hope everyone takes what

00:40:25.760 --> 00:40:27.110
Mr. Huang just said seriously.

00:40:27.590 --> 00:40:28.920
We need to ensure both

00:40:29.230 --> 00:40:30.630
quality and schedule.

00:40:31.400 --> 00:40:32.030
Of course,

00:40:32.480 --> 00:40:33.880
I don't want to fire anyone.

00:40:34.110 --> 00:40:35.190
But you all need to work hard.

00:40:35.590 --> 00:40:36.590
Don't let me down.

00:40:37.190 --> 00:40:38.150
Order volume has increased.

00:40:38.710 --> 00:40:40.670
We will open more production lines.

00:40:41.230 --> 00:40:42.550
I will be too busy to handle everything.

00:40:42.880 --> 00:40:44.360
Therefore, Mr. Huang wants

00:40:45.110 --> 00:40:46.280
to select an assistant head.

00:40:47.480 --> 00:40:48.030
Mr. Huang,

00:40:48.480 --> 00:40:49.400
you should announce it.

00:40:49.670 --> 00:40:50.150
Okay.

00:40:54.550 --> 00:40:55.280
I announce

00:40:55.590 --> 00:40:57.070
the assistant head

00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:04.070
is the excellent employee,

00:41:04.070 --> 00:41:05.030
Ms. Xu A'nan!

00:41:08.760 --> 00:41:09.760
Congratulations, Nan!

00:41:09.800 --> 00:41:10.630
Congratulations, Nan!

00:41:10.670 --> 00:41:12.150
Nan, you're amazing!

00:41:13.440 --> 00:41:14.510
Thank you, Mr. Huang.

00:41:14.590 --> 00:41:16.030
I will definitely lead the girls

00:41:16.070 --> 00:41:16.920
to work hard

00:41:17.280 --> 00:41:18.360
and complete the order.

00:41:18.880 --> 00:41:19.400
Keep it up!

00:41:20.110 --> 00:41:20.760
Mr. Huang,

00:41:21.400 --> 00:41:22.110
about the assistant head...

00:41:22.630 --> 00:41:23.760
I've discussed the promotion

00:41:23.760 --> 00:41:24.960
of assistant head

00:41:24.960 --> 00:41:25.760
with the other leaders.

00:41:25.960 --> 00:41:27.230
They all agree it should be Nan.

00:41:28.840 --> 00:41:29.280
Come on,

00:41:29.590 --> 00:41:31.360
let's applaud Ms. Xu.

00:41:45.440 --> 00:41:46.400
It's clear

00:41:47.030 --> 00:41:48.550
Ms. Zhang still supports you.

00:41:50.280 --> 00:41:51.840
I can tell too.

00:41:53.150 --> 00:41:54.480
But Mr. Huang said

00:41:55.400 --> 00:41:56.150
it was a decision made

00:41:56.150 --> 00:41:57.670
by all the leaders together.

00:41:58.320 --> 00:41:59.480
Li couldn't do anything about it.

00:42:00.320 --> 00:42:01.510
She apologized to me,

00:42:01.510 --> 00:42:03.110
which made me feel bad.

00:42:03.630 --> 00:42:05.480
What other leaders?

00:42:06.030 --> 00:42:06.710
In our factory,

00:42:06.710 --> 00:42:08.320
Huang Yaodong calls the shots.

00:42:11.150 --> 00:42:12.030
Have you noticed

00:42:12.030 --> 00:42:13.760
anything between Xu A'nan and him?

00:42:14.280 --> 00:42:15.480
Did you notice their eye contact?

00:42:16.510 --> 00:42:17.550
Don't speculate.

00:42:18.110 --> 00:42:19.480
I'm not.

00:42:19.550 --> 00:42:20.440
It's just a gut feeling.

00:42:21.920 --> 00:42:23.920
Using an improper
relationship to get ahead.

00:42:25.030 --> 00:42:25.880
Stop.

00:42:26.590 --> 00:42:27.800
You can say that at home,

00:42:27.800 --> 00:42:28.320
but you can't

00:42:28.320 --> 00:42:29.760
say it at the factory.

00:42:30.480 --> 00:42:31.960
Everyone works hard.

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:32.880
We can't let rumors

00:42:32.880 --> 00:42:33.960
ruin a girl's life.

00:42:35.440 --> 00:42:36.320
Look at me.

00:42:36.400 --> 00:42:37.960
Why am I acting like this now?

00:42:40.800 --> 00:42:41.670
Alright.

00:42:41.710 --> 00:42:43.440
I'll get cleaned and cook for you.

00:42:45.590 --> 00:42:46.190
Go clean yourself.

00:42:46.230 --> 00:42:47.190
Just wait to eat.

00:42:47.550 --> 00:42:48.150
You're cooking?

00:42:48.760 --> 00:42:49.510
Cooking what?

00:42:49.710 --> 00:42:50.920
You'll see when you get back.